{"tid":1632094,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，唔係淨係要加油，唔係淨係要反抗，係要贏！","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:43.000Z","uid":207805,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"47a2c2e8c2d225801e99e20ebf13dbeae67718ae","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:40.000Z","msg":"拜託 唔好成日講咩<br />\n<strong>「俾著人地國家啲人已經xxxx」</strong><br />\n<strong>「xxx革命人地已經xxxx 香港人淨係係度xxx 唉...」</strong><br />\n黃背心呀 烏克蘭呀 仲有好多好多例子 <br />\n最後個結果唔係好架 人地個過程好悲慘 <br />\n比我地慘好多倍<br />\n人地個代價好大架<br />\n你係咪想<strong>香港個結果好似佢地咁</strong>？<br />\n你係咪承受得起個代價？<br />\n<br />\n講近啲 印尼學運<br />\n個政府有幾極權 個修例有幾惡<br />\n全世界都知<br />\n但人地群起反抗 燒埋政府大樓咁勁啦<br />\n歐美傳媒報過幾多 有冇領導人出聲撐過<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>係 冇 人 理 呀！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n但點解我地前排舉下旗行下領事館 唱下歌<br />\n咁多國際報章報導 有領導人出聲支持？<br />\n個現實就係咁 <br />\n我地香港嘅<ins><strong>獨特身分、地位、價值同檔次</strong></ins><br />\n都俾果啲第三世界 / 次級歐美國家高<br />\n當我地可以用更容易 更好嘅方式<br />\n去攞到更加好嘅結果<br />\n更重要係我地值得更好嘅時候<br />\n點解唔做？<br />\n點解要<del><strong>自貶</strong></del> 用<strong>落後國家嘅方法</strong>抗爭？<br />\n(apology to those countries but that&rsquo;s the reality<br />\n<br />\n前排唔係好興奮係咁煲<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">人權民主法案</span></strong>架咩<br />\n宜家又唔理 擺埋佢一邊 唔繼續爭取支持 做其他野<br />\n你咪因為其實你地根本都唔信人地幫到手？<br />\n或者帶<strong><del>政治潔癖</del></strong>不齒求人地幫手？<br />\n當你都唔知有咩更加好嘅方法嘅時候<br />\n點解唔落力試下呢條路 努力爭取<br />\n等多一陣睇下個法案係咪真係幫到手？<br />\n<strong>靜靜地贏唔得？</strong><br />\n我地明明有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">國際玩法 黃金套路</span></strong>可以玩<br />\n點解要俾港共shift左我地去<strong><del>香港玩法</del></strong>？<br />\n<br />\n最後 堅持<strong>不割蓆</strong>、 <strong>不譴責</strong><br />\n但唔代表<strong>不用腦</strong>、<strong>不反省</strong> 唔諗下有冇更好嘅方法<br />\n道德上 我對宜家嘅事冇意見 我地都冇資格judge<br />\n我只係覺得目標上 成效上 宜家嘅做法係咪真係最好<br />\n我地出嚟唔係淨係為左啖氣 為左尊嚴<br />\n唔係淨係為左<strong><del>「寧為玉碎 不為瓦全」</del></strong><br />\n我地係為左贏架<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">落得戰場就要為左贏 就要諗點贏</span></strong><br />\n贏唔贏到係一回事 唔係為左贏就唔好打呢場杖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港人 </strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">要</span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">贏</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"47f079d4e7138ca73397d9f6eed4cdb9ef0d42bb","tid":1632094,"uid":15259,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"e54e6588c1eb6dced216bc4effe33073e3243b9c","tid":1632094,"uid":287211,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},{"pid":"a822e49e5fc8d82cf89de07aaee610dc56a4c45b","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:25.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"402879e76600be9d4cd28faa7abb3265cfd56e56","tid":1632094,"uid":69761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzE523y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzE523y.jpg&h=1a0e2ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKw4zaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKw4zaf.jpg&h=43348a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pr7jn3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpr7jn3B.jpg&h=0499d221&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9726d0df300c1ea2bae6bd5266a52baa66371a20","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"3809ce0463b12f06247a3072401018f503c0a835","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:08.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"20085067ac21da5725b0c07d103a8a848a25164a","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:28.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"3d9b1cdcc657befcc5f84e305978b4479ee644f7","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"5/10"},{"pid":"dc0f01bb25d23006156dc252ec16ca15a1dc848a","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:49.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"bf4eae71ff98993a198f1bd1ab8cf125062ae1d2","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:15.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"b8246729ba56eb7042c8a765742e65dd66c07a6c","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"dfbe148046831038ac2da95f8fb33a079c743531","tid":1632094,"uid":301079,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"402879e76600be9d4cd28faa7abb3265cfd56e56","tid":1632094,"uid":69761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MzE523y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMzE523y.jpg&h=1a0e2ac7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zKw4zaf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzKw4zaf.jpg&h=43348a61&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pr7jn3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpr7jn3B.jpg&h=0499d221&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:59.000Z","msg":"真係有心硬闖既到佢唔俾入咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759eba40f486df03931817dab09fb3d933a54941","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"d593709fa27a5a940090fc945cd08ae82c48d41a","tid":1632094,"uid":207805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:59.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"7f4bd21526c4cba2ef0807e6291adf0cf771283b","tid":1632094,"uid":10042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"推啊屌"},{"pid":"013a9c2953c880cd62171c0997f3426e520036a3","tid":1632094,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"推啊推 讓這post推"},{"pid":"21a3a4e6d2b195d89dbc95de47a621667289b16a","tid":1632094,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:12.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4489052711e552dd8c070448044f67c40bab32c8","tid":1632094,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"目光睇遠啲 最緊要達成最終目的 其他係支線"},{"pid":"f1fadfbdd44f2d81519c3f2a5e74f19f5739e963","tid":1632094,"uid":331388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:22:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aa3e493ef2e8a2c1eb1faff6560ef7ba52e53b0","tid":1632094,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！ 而家只係要你入黎推post</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6b0edd9b868f415fee7503fe2a46b2a851e6d4ee","tid":1632094,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:17.000Z","msg":"要贏大戰場人權法<br />\n唔好執著係緊急法呢個小戰場<br />\n<br />\n18區唱歌呀"},{"pid":"2d0e096dfea7f3733707691bcc84714870cfbab4","tid":1632094,"uid":129617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:41.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"5c7cdb8b9aeffa644adfb0e961afb3a04ea19c91","tid":1632094,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:54.000Z","msg":"唔好沉迷喺仇恨 贏咗先清算"},{"pid":"7b992f38bad531a9d3c98808fdacfd43b362defd","tid":1632094,"uid":14188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:17:43.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}